item.title: Working with me
item.description: If you are in need of some temporary, part-time freelance work (that is, you don’t mind me working in the evenings! I do have a full-time job I’m not interested in leaving!), please get in touch. I’m familiar with a wide variety of languages, frameworks, tools, and platforms.
